Producing the lexica:

  % cd GF/lib/src/
  % gf
  > i finnish/DictFin.gf
  > gt -cat=VK | l -list | wf -file=verbsFin.txt
  > gt -cat=NK | l -list | wf -file=nounsFin.txt
  > gt -cat=AK | l -list | wf -file=adjectivesFin.txt


Lexicon sizes:

  % wc *.txt
    1467   14670  193296 adjectivesFin.txt
   25414  254660 3322151 nounsFin.txt
    9498  113976 1389272 verbsFin.txt
   36379  383306 4904719 total

  % runghc MkExLex <verbsFin.txt >verbs.txt


